body_html:
Hi @sibyjackgrove,

Thanks for the interest on TF-TRT integration. Currently the integration is still in progress and we're actively working on it. The API is not stable yet and may change in the future. You may want to take a look at the test/test_tftrt.py script mentioned in the README, which is in https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/blob/master/tensorflow/contrib/tensorrt/test/test_tftrt.py. I'll leave to @samikama about the documentation.

body:
Hi @sibyjackgrove,

Thanks for the interest on TF-TRT integration. Currently the integration is still in progress and we're actively working on it. The API is not stable yet and may change in the future. You may want to take a look at the `test/test_tftrt.py` script mentioned in the README, which is in https://github.com/tensorflow/tensorflow/blob/master/tensorflow/contrib/tensorrt/test/test_tftrt.py. I'll leave to @samikama about the documentation.
